    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/47ae47ec00d841c88c49b7c45864b305.avif?t=1734023045\" width=621 height=165 /></span><br><br>Hello! Welcome to the ranger system! I'll be your guide throughout the Steam page.<br>Firstly, I'll give you a rundown of your basic moves.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shooting</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/e5ec217995973c95d523f65db3b91f35.poster.avif?t=1734023045\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/e5ec217995973c95d523f65db3b91f35.webm?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/e5ec217995973c95d523f65db3b91f35.mp4?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Candy, you can shoot bullets sideways.<br>Mint can shoot them vertically.<br>Plum shoots them back and forth.<br>And lastly, Lemon’s bullets can clear diagonal formations.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Melee attack</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/c78d8515b55537b3ff119cf4386e7746.poster.avif?t=1734023045\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/c78d8515b55537b3ff119cf4386e7746.webm?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/c78d8515b55537b3ff119cf4386e7746.mp4?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your weapon is not merely a gun! Parry or hook to special objects to advance through the levels!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Jump, Dash and Brake</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/54fb872de50dc1cabbc792a1f110d0fb.poster.avif?t=1734023045\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/54fb872de50dc1cabbc792a1f110d0fb.webm?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/54fb872de50dc1cabbc792a1f110d0fb.mp4?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Jump over obstacles, dash to go faster or brake if you're feeling overwhelmed!<br><br>Let's go over every reward you can earn on each level now. They are as follow:<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ranking</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/09117e59d9aa265afa7f943ed9427144.poster.avif?t=1734023045\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/09117e59d9aa265afa7f943ed9427144.webm?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/09117e59d9aa265afa7f943ed9427144.mp4?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Score 5 stars ranks!</strong><br>You will be ranked based on your<br>performance.<br>Try not to break the chain or get hit as that will hurt your ranking!<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Memories</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/7be9f6b1ce4f75018295d111111f001b.poster.avif?t=1734023045\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/7be9f6b1ce4f75018295d111111f001b.webm?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/7be9f6b1ce4f75018295d111111f001b.mp4?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get a memory picture everytime you clear a level with a high score!<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ranger Medals</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/59bc7175f774d0d2dedff78cd681ef02.poster.avif?t=1734023045\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/59bc7175f774d0d2dedff78cd681ef02.webm?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226270/extras/59bc7175f774d0d2dedff78cd681ef02.mp4?t=1734023045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Find ranger medals!<br>They unlock levels and sometimes even boss encounters!<br><br>And that's about it! I'll let you discover everything else as you go! Good luck!<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo Features</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Up to 6 playable levels.</strong><br></li><li><strong>4 playable characters.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Split your team to take on 2 paths at the same time!</strong></li></ul>",
